snippet.title: Best VGM 1417 - Monster Hunter Tri - Tremble of the Sea and Land ~ Lagiacrus
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii / Wii U / 3DS
Monster Hunter Tri (2009)
Tremble of the Sea and Land ~ Lagiacrus
Yuko Komiyama
